Apple red and green start are bright The apple trees are tall The leaves are small The apples
fall in autumn time
When you get to the cores inside the cores are pips you throw the cores on the fire to burn then
the boys in our village go in the orchard and climb the trees and pinch them
all then they run away with them
then the earwigs fall out in their pockets
the apples are sweet
the trees are full of apples
some of them are cookers
the apples are so gay hanging on the trees
with the sun on them
no wonder the boys like pinch them

What I am going to do when I leave school
When I leave I want to be a hairdresser in Melton or Tonbury
or I want to work in a shop
I do not want to get married till I am twenty one
When I have children I am going to leave work and the husband has got to like children and take them out
I want twins
and I want four bridesmaids
I want to live in a bungalow
for my holiday I would like to go to Butlins , for a honeymoon I like to go to Scotland

